<title><%= title %></title>
<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-20 px-6 fade-in">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-black text-secondary mb-6">Fitur Unggulan</h1>
        <p class="text-slate-500 text-lg">Eksplorasi apa yang bisa Anda lakukan dengan ekosistem PuZero.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-lightning text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">AI Chat Performa Tinggi</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Gunakan model Gemini 3 Flash terbaru untuk membantu coding, menulis artikel, atau sekadar teman ngobrol yang cerdas.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-pink-500/10 text-pink-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-download-simple text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">Multi-Platform Downloader</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Unduh video dari YouTube, Instagram Reels, TikTok tanpa watermark, hingga video dari X (Twitter) dalam hitungan detik dengan kualitas original.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-indigo-500/10 text-indigo-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-layout text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">Modern & SPA-like</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Navigasi antar halaman terasa sangat cepat tanpa reload penuh berkat integrasi teknologi HTMX dan desain yang responsif.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="p-8 bg-white rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
                <i class="ph-bold ph-shield-check text-2xl"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary mb-3">Privasi & Keamanan</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">Semua riwayat chat disimpan secara lokal di browser Anda. Kami tidak menyimpan data sensitif atau file unduhan Anda di server kami.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>